metadata.name: Louisa Verity Cannon- Cyborg Woman of 2050
metadata.description:
Title:

Louisa Verity Cannon- Cyborg Woman of 2050

Artist:

Mike Sherratt

Edition:

1/1

Description:

This is the first major collection that Mike has started to feel his style of art coming to life. He updated opensea with two outstanding collections and now he presents.

Cyborg Woman of 2050

Ten pieces were all brought to life from things that Mike created using AI tech and then manipulated with Photoshop.

We hope you enjoy the pieces and have time to visit Mike's diverse collections.

Collector will unlock an image once purchased.
